data.title: VeriSign Acquires inCode Wireless
data.meta_description: VeriSign, Inc announced it has signed a definitive agreement to acquire inCode Wireless, a global business and technology consulting firm. inCode has become a global force in wireless business and technology consulting, with 14 offices in 10 countries. The company provides strategy consulting services to nearly every major wireless, wireline, cable operator and telecom equipment manufacturer, as well as leading enterprises.
